#
#   Method 2: CLI (automated)
#     - Run: chmod +x vercel-env-setup.sh
#     - Run: ./vercel-env-setup.sh
#
#   Method 3: Manual CLI
#     - vercel env add VARIABLE_NAME production preview
#
# AFTER ADDING VARIABLES:
#   - Vercel will automatically trigger a new deployment
